875
01:29:24.526 --> 01:29:27.237
My journey is to bring back Kung Lao.

876
01:29:28.113 --> 01:29:29.656
This is not the end.

877
01:29:31.950 --> 01:29:33.660
It is only the beginning.

878
01:29:51.428 --> 01:29:52.428
